---
import Card from '../Card.astro'
import type { HTMLTag } from 'astro/types'
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I'm a Product Specialist currently exploring new opportunities.
      Previously at Freightify, I led product strategy and development for digital freight pricing solutions,
      overseeing the development of multiple reporting solutions and building AI agents to automate workflows and insights,
      bridging the gap between business needs and technical implementation to drive innovation in global logistics.
      <br />
      <br />
      My expertise includes:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm font-light ml-2 space-y-1">
      <li>Product Strategy & Roadmapping</li>
      <li>Agile Project Management</li>
      <li>User Research & Analytics</li>
      <li>Technical Product Management</li>
      <li>Cross-functional Team Leadership</li>
      <li>Data-Driven Decision Making</li>
      <li>AI Agents & Automation</li>
      <li>Reporting & BI</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p class="text-sm font-light mt-4">
      Beyond product management, I'm passionate about building user-centric products that drive business outcomes.
      I specialize in translating complex technical capabilities into valuable product experiences.
      When I'm not working on products, you'll find me exploring markets, engaging with users,
      and staying updated with the latest in technology and product innovation.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Product Strategy</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Agile</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">User Research</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Analytics</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Leadership</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Tech PM</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">AI Agents</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-md">Reporting</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>
